<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Crunchy Bites | Restaurant</title>

    <meta name="description" content="Crunchy Bites Restaurant - Fresh, Crispy & Delicious Food">

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/6c6b6b6b6b.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</head>

<body>

<!-- ================= NAVBAR ================= -->

<header>

<div class="logo">
🍔 <span>Crunchy Bites</span>
</div>

<nav>

<a href="#home">Home</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#menu">Menu</a>
<a href="#gallery">Gallery</a>
<a href="#reviews">Reviews</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>

</nav>

<a href="#contact" class="book-btn">
Order Now
</a>

</header>

<!-- ================= HERO ================= -->

<section class="hero" id="home">

<div class="overlay"></div>

<div class="hero-content">

<h1>
Taste The Best
<span>Burgers & Fast Food</span>
</h1>

<p>
Fresh Ingredients • Amazing Taste • Fast Delivery
</p>

<div class="hero-buttons">

<a href="#menu" class="btn">
View Menu
</a>

<a href="#contact" class="btn2">
Book Table
</a>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- ================= FEATURES ================= -->

<section class="features">

<div class="feature">

<div class="icon">🍔</div>

<h3>Fresh Food</h3>

<p>Prepared daily using premium ingredients.</p>

</div>

<div class="feature">

<div class="icon">🚚</div>

<h3>Fast Delivery</h3>

<p>Quick delivery to your doorstep.</p>

</div>

<div class="feature">

<div class="icon">⭐</div>

<h3>Top Rated</h3>

<p>Loved by hundreds of happy customers.</p>

</div>

<div class="feature">

<div class="icon">👨‍🍳</div>

<h3>Expert Chefs</h3>

<p>Food prepared by experienced chefs.</p>

</div>

</section>

<!-- ================= ABOUT ================= -->

<section class="about" id="about">

<div class="about-image">

<img src="images/about.jpg" alt="Restaurant">

</div>

<div class="about-text">

<h4>About Crunchy Bites</h4>

<h2>Serving Happiness One Bite At A Time</h2>

<p>

Crunchy Bites is your favorite destination for delicious burgers,
crispy fries, pizzas, wraps, sandwiches, beverages, and much more.

Every dish is made fresh with quality ingredients and served with
excellent hospitality.

</p>

<div class="stats">

<div>

<h3>10+</h3>

<span>Food Items</span>

</div>

<div>

<h3>500+</h3>

<span>Happy Customers</span>

</div>

<div>

<h3>4.8★</h3>

<span>Customer Rating</span>

</div>

</div>

<a href="#menu" class="btn">
Explore Menu
</a>

</div>

</section>

<!-- ================= MENU ================= -->

<section class="menu" id="menu">

<h4>Our Menu</h4>

<h2>Popular Dishes</h2>

<div class="menu-grid">

<div class="menu-card">

<img src="images/burger.jpg">

<h3>Cheese Burger</h3>

<p>Loaded with cheese and grilled patty.</p>

<h4>₹149</h4>

<button>Order</button>

</div>

<div class="menu-card">

<img src="images/pizza.jpg">

<h3>Veg Pizza</h3>

<p>Fresh vegetables with mozzarella cheese.</p>

<h4>₹299</h4>

<button>Order</button>

</div>

<div class="menu-card">

<img src="images/fries.jpg">

<h3>French Fries</h3>

<p>Golden crispy fries served hot.</p>

<h4>₹99</h4>

<button>Order</button>

</div>

<div class="menu-card">

<img src="images/shake.jpg">

<h3>Chocolate Shake</h3>

<p>Rich creamy chocolate milkshake.</p>

<h4>₹129</h4>

<button>Order</button>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- Gallery, Reviews, Contact and Footer will be added in Part 2 -->

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
